text: Æt Hansfleote gæð þæra twegra bisceoprice togædere, fram Hansfleote to hoingdene, fram hoingdene to Tumwyllan, fram Tumwyllan to sandhlincan, fram sandhlincan andlanges þær ea to þære wic, fram þære wic to þære cortan, and swa andlanges to Suðsexan.
Þus hyt stynt and æfre gyt stod buton se arcebisceop hwæs geunnon wille of hys dæle þam oðran bisceope.
